			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Utterly, utterly useless.<BR>
<BR>
For those who don't know, there are lots of free ways to check which way is north.<BR>
<BR>
The easiest way to check in most zones is look up.  Not only can you watch the sun or moon, but clouds only move in one direction.<BR>
<BR>
If you can't see the sky, drop a sword on the ground.  The tip of the blade points north when it lands.
				</font>
